<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 43px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">周雨晴，女，汉族，共青团员，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 43px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">2001年11月生，江西吉安人，2020年9月入学。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 43px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">寒假期间，她积极响应校团委号召，报名参与大学生</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 43px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">“返家乡”社会实践活动，在中国共青团吉州区委进行政务实践。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 43px; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">在实习期间，她主要负责新闻采写、拍照录像、图文编排、材料撰写、组织策划、活动跟进等工作。负责吉州区共青团微信号公众平台以及视频号的运营。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 43px; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2n18Qa8gmEIZHPicqGZs6LL0QqEnwXYAvibHNQosRYzU8cUVIuKOibaUf9Jno32eNiclcBjOfuy9Nl7yNZDAtfZFwQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="261" height="187" style="width: 261px; height: 187px;"/></span></p><p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="121695" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: center;"><section data-width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 585px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(217, 17, 17); height: 1px; overflow: hidden;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(251, 246, 239);"><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">凝聚正能量，讲好“青”故事。来到团区委的第一天，我就认识到共青团的工作不是纸上谈兵的，不是闷在办公室的，共青团工作是有温度、有速度、有力度、有深度、有厚度的。在“希望工程·壹元捐”、守护母亲河“河小青”行动、童心港湾等活动时，我不但参与了活动的组织策划和跟进，还与青年志愿者们一起投入到实践中去，宣传党的政策，进行文明劝导，奉献一份爱心。每每实践后，我都感到心灵清澈、生活充实，这种幸福感，来自基层一线。我将以此次实践经历为新起点，总结经验，将实践所学所得运用到接下来的学习和工作中去；刻苦学习，努力专研，不断提升，以更好的精神面貌积极投身服务同学、服务家乡、服务社会的实践中去，以奋斗姿态激昂青春，不负时代不负华年。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">——B200504周雨晴</span></p></section></section></section></section></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(251, 246, 239); text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p>